R. G. Niederhoffer Capital Management, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 22, 2017 4:00 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of R. G. Niederhoffer Capital Management, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
R. G. Niederhoffer Capital Management, Inc. is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to corporations. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It invests in public equity, fixed income, currency, and commodity markets across the globe. The firm also invests in derivatives including spot currencies, futures contracts, forward contracts, swaps, and options. It employs quantitative analysis to make its investments. It obtains external research to complement its in-house research to make its investments. R. G. Niederhoffer Capital Management, Inc. was founded in 1993 and is based in New York City.


1700 Broadway39th FloorNew York, NY 10019United StatesFounded in 1993



Phone: 212-245-0400

